                <p class="lead">I have loved basketball since I was a little kid. Using EJS, CSS, Bootstrap, JavaScript, Node.js, Express, and Axios, I created this website to fetch data from a third-party API. This website allows users to search for player details using their first name.</p>
                <h5 class="mb-3 mt-5  ccontent">Hoping to Achieve</h5>
                <p class="lead">I enjoy challenging myself in every way possible. Once I set my mind to something, I need to see it through. I completed a Bachelor's degree in Computer Science before moving to Australia. Recently I received my Permanent Residency, I am eager to revisit web development. I hope this project showcases my skills and demonstrates my ability to contribute to the success of my next employment. I am confident in my ability to use these skills to achieve great results.</p>
                
